PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue designating the following countries as "designated states" for the purposes of the Visiting Forces Act, and declaring that the Act, except Part VI, shall apply to them. . 1. Republic of Benin - République du Bénin 2. Republic of El Salvador - République d'El Salvador 3. Republic of Estonia - République d'Estonie 4. Republic of Latvia - République de Lettonie 5. Republic of Lithuania - République de Lituanie 6. Republic of Nicaragua - République du Nicaragua 7. Romania - Roumanie .
